#: ../../source/vuln/sql/classify.rst:2
msgid "注入分类"
msgstr "Injection Classification"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/classify.rst:5
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Overview"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/classify.rst:6
msgid ""
"SQL注入是一种代码注入技术，用于攻击数据驱动的应用程序。 "
"在应用程序中，如果没有做恰当的过滤，则可能使得恶意的SQL语句被插入输入字段中执行（例如将数据库内容转储给攻击者）。"
msgstr ""
"SQL injection is a code injection technique used to attack data-driven "
"applications. If an application does not apply proper filtering, malicious "
"SQL statements may be inserted into input fields and executed, for example "
"to dump database contents to an attacker."

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/classify.rst:10
msgid "按技巧分类"
msgstr "Classification by Technique"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/classify.rst:11
msgid "根据使用的技巧，SQL注入类型可分为"
msgstr "Based on the technique used, SQL injection can be classified as:"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/classify.rst:13
msgid "盲注"
msgstr "Blind injection"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/classify.rst:14
msgid "布尔盲注：只能从应用返回中推断语句执行后的布尔值"
msgstr "Boolean-based blind injection: the Boolean result of a statement can only be inferred from the application's response"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/classify.rst:15
msgid "时间盲注：应用没有明确的回显，只能使用特定的时间函数来判断"
msgstr "Time-based blind injection: the application has no explicit echo, so specific time functions are used for judgment"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/classify.rst:16
msgid "报错注入：应用会显示全部或者部分的报错信息"
msgstr "Error-based injection: the application displays all or part of the error information"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/classify.rst:17
msgid "堆叠注入：有的应用可以加入 ``;`` 后一次执行多条语句"
msgstr "Stacked injection: some applications allow multiple statements to be executed in one request after adding ``;``"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/classify.rst:18
msgid "其他"
msgstr "Other"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/classify.rst:21
msgid "按获取数据的方式分类"
msgstr "Classification by Data Retrieval Method"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/classify.rst:22
msgid "另外也可以根据获取数据的方式分为3类"
msgstr "SQL injection can also be divided into three categories by the way data is retrieved:"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/classify.rst:25
msgid "inband"
msgstr "in-band"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/classify.rst:26
msgid "利用Web应用来直接获取数据，如报错注入，这类注入都是通过站点的响应或者错误反馈来提取数据。"
msgstr "Use the web application to retrieve data directly, such as error-based injection. This category extracts data through site responses or error feedback."

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/classify.rst:29
msgid "inference"
msgstr "inference"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/classify.rst:30
msgid "通过Web的一些反映来推断数据，如布尔盲注，也就是我们通俗的盲注， 通过web应用的其他改变来推断数据。"
msgstr "Infer data from web-side behavior, such as Boolean-based blind injection. In common usage this is blind injection, where data is inferred from other changes in the web application."

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/classify.rst:34
msgid "out of band (OOB)"
msgstr "out-of-band (OOB)"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/classify.rst:35
msgid "通过其他传输方式来获得数据，比如DNS解析协议和电子邮件。"
msgstr "Retrieve data through another transport channel, such as DNS resolution or email."
